{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:07.441Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/445\n\n## Problem\nIn a tag-heavy workspace ~43% of `pm context` brief output (1970 of 4582 B) is repeated `tags:` blocks — siblings inherit the parent tag set and repeat it verbatim per row. No --no-tags; brief depth cannot drop tags.\n\n## Proposed fix\n(1) `--no-tags` on context (and honor --fields projection, shipped via PR#297); (2) inherited-tag folding: when all low_level children share the parent tag set, emit tags once on the parent (or `tags_inherited: true`); (3) consider tag-less rows as the brief-depth default.\n\n## Definition of done\nContext size in this workspace cut ~40% at brief depth with no loss for the next-work decision; spec pins folding semantics; MCP pm_context parity; docs updated."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-ishm"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-445: suppress/factor repeated inherited tags in pm context rows (--no-tags + tag folding)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-445: 43% of pm context brief output is repeated inherited tags blocks; add --no-tags and inherited-tag folding. Duplicate check: searched context tags/token — GH-435 item covers JSON nulls, this covers tag repetition; no other overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","gh-issue","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:07.441Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:07.441Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":120},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"context supports --no-tags; inherited tag sets folded to parent row (or tags_inherited marker); ~40% brief-depth size cut measured here; MCP parity; spec pins folding semantics"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"bc6db536bcea39ee939ae3bb6d8f1b837ecc73f34cd56743af31f3ec0b45ad87","message":""}
